(322, 'options_carousel_0_text', 'Step into a world of wellness and self-discovery with Stephanie Corneille, a seasoned Wellness Enthusiast. With over 15 years of professional dance and two decades of Pilates experience, Stephanie goes beyond the physical. As a certified Keto nutrition coach, she nurtures holistic well-being. Step into Stephanie\'s Pilates sanctuary - a transformative space where stress is channeled and transformed. Join her on a journey to wholeness, unlocking your full potential through movement, mindfulness, and nourishment.', 'no'),
