(330, 'options_carousel_1_text', 'Embark on a transformative journey with Mihail, a seasoned Self Development Expert. With a childhood passion for psychology and training in elite special forces, Mihail brings over 30 years of experience. From dreams and autogenic training to super-discipline, he guides students in self-regulation, stress management, and achieving balance. Anyone who joins his practice, overcomes challenges, and reaches new heights.', 'no'),
(331, '_options_carousel_1_text', 'field_661f8a942551f', 'no'),
