(337, '_options_carousel_2_profession', 'field_661e360ae3a94', 'no'),
(338, 'options_carousel_2_text', 'With 20 years in the corporate world, Ruth transitioned her life by embracing the Wim Hof Method. As a certified instructor, she conducts workshops for diverse age groups, promoting physical and mental well-being. Ruth organizes events and retreats, customizing experiences with mindful activities. Her burnout coaching integrates Wim Hof Method principles. Committed to giving back, Ruth collaborates with charities like St Mungo\'s and NHS East, enhancing the well-being of marginalized communities and healthcare professionals.', 'no'),
