(346, 'options_carousel_3_text', 'With a diverse background spanning across cultures, Sandra’s culinary expertise shines through various roles, from consulting at renowned establishments like Fata Morgana Restaurant in Amorgos to crafting creative baking at Holy Llama in Athens. From her early days at Vasilikos Grill House to her current role as a private chef, Sandra\'s passion for food is evident. Her philosophy: infuse every dish with freshness, healthfulness, and seasonal goodness. As a private chef, she\'s catered to prestigious events, including those hosted by embassies. Sandra\'s dedication to fresh, seasonal ingredients and her artistic sensibility brings a unique flair to her dishes, reflecting her multicultural upbringing and extensive travels. Her culinary creations are not only flavorful but also visually stunning and culturally rich.', 'no'),
